data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Beautiful home placed in a quiet neighborhood overlooking a POND! This 3 bedroom/2 bathroom home features an abundance of windows brightening the house throughout, tall ceilings with gorgeous beams in living room, a great layout with bedrooms having their own wing apart from the main living space. Master suite having access to back deck. Enjoy a covered back patio/deck overlooking the green space while entertaining guests or spending your mornings taking in the beauty. Come see this for yourself!
